[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man found dead in Ballater Street in Glasgow

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been found dead in a Glasgow street.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
His body was discovered on Ballater Street in the Gorbals at about 17:10 on Saturday.
Police said they were treating his death as "unexplained".
A Police Scotland spokesman said the man was still to be formally identified. A post mortem examination will be carried out to establish the cause of death and a report sent to the procurator fiscal.
